room_title: Escape room "Dinosaur" by Time Travel Escapes in West Palm Beach
room_description: The melting of the permafrost tundra in the Arctic due to global climate change has released a deadly virus from prehistoric times. The world is in danger of experiencing one of the worst pandemics in recorded history. Our lab has determined that a dinosaur was immune to this virus, and we sent a team back in time to retrieve enough DNA for us to figure out why so we can make a vaccine. They have gone missing and you must find all the research they left behind.
